                    WOW, Jim was happy to see the samples, they looked great. Thank you for your efforts to get this accomplished.
                    Please pass along my appreciation and gratitude to all parties involved.
                </p>
                
                <span class="absolute -bottom-12 right-0 text-6xl font-serif text-amber-500/30 select-none pointer-events-none">”</span>
            </div>

            <div>
                <a href="/oscar/request-a-quote" class="home-rfq-button">
